    ‚ąá (names parents scriptitems)‚ÜźGetFileTiesIn rootns;all;allrefs;mask;parents;r;t;urefs
     ‚ćĚ Find all file system links to objects below rootns
      allrefs‚Üź2‚äÉ¬®all‚Üź5177‚Ć∂‚ć¨
      t‚Üźurefs‚Üź‚ą™allrefs
      mask‚Üź(‚ČĘurefs)‚ćī0
      :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘt ‚čĄ :Repeat
              mask‚ą®‚Üź(‚ćē¬®t)‚ąä(‚äā‚ćērootns) ‚ćĚ Have we reached rootns?  - ‚ćē because of mantis 18147
              :If t‚Č°t.## ‚čĄ :Leave ‚čĄ :EndIf  ‚ćĚ continue until everything is root
              t‚Üźt.##         ‚ćĚ Move all pointers up to parent
          :EndRepeat ‚čĄ :EndIf
      :If 0=‚ČĘr‚Üź(allrefs‚ąämask/urefs)/all ‚ćĚ selection of 5177‚Ć∂‚ć¨
          names‚Üź0‚ćī‚äā'' ‚čĄ parents‚Üź0‚ćī# ‚čĄ scriptitems‚Üź‚ć¨
      :Else
          names‚Üź‚ćē¬®1‚äÉ¬®r
          parents‚Üź‚ćé¬®‚ćē¬®2‚äÉ¬®r ‚ćĚ need ‚ćé¬®‚ćē¬® because of mantis 18147
          scriptitems‚ÜźIsScripted EachUnique parents  ‚ćĚ parent is scripted ‚Üí item is a script item
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá r‚ÜźRemoveFileTiesIn rootns;names;parents;scriptitems
     ‚ćĚ Find all file system links to objects below rootns, and remove using 5178‚Ć∂
     ‚ćĚ Return number of links broken
      (names parents scriptitems)‚ÜźGetFileTiesIn rootns ‚ćĚ links to be removed
      ‚ćĚ there might be some orphaned script items - interpreter must forget about them
      ‚ćĚ do it first because of mantis 18606
      :If 1‚ąäscriptitems ‚ćĚ script items are simply untied
          {}(scriptitems/parents){‚ćļ.(5178‚Ć∂)‚ćĶ}¬®(scriptitems/names)
      :EndIf
      :If 0‚ąäscriptitems  ‚ćĚ scripts are more complicated because of Mantis 18148
          r‚Üź+/((~scriptitems)/parents)Untie¬®((~scriptitems)/names)
      :Else
          r‚Üź0
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá changed‚ÜźFileHasChanged(ns name file filesrc);compsrc;file2;hash;line;lines;name2;nameref;nc;parent;ts;nc2;aplsrc
      compsrc‚Üź0 ‚čĄ changed‚Üź0
      (name2 parent nc2 file2 line lines hash ts)‚Üźns.(5179‚Ć∂)name  ‚ćĚ name2 may be a name or a ref - parent is a ref
      :If 0=nc‚Üźns NameClass name ‚čĄ changed‚Üź1  ‚ćĚ name not defined - need to update from file
      :ElseIf 0‚ąä‚ćīname2 ‚čĄ compsrc‚Üź1 ‚ćĚ not tied at all - need to compare sources directly
      :ElseIf file‚ČĘfile2 ‚čĄ changed‚Üź1  ‚ćĚ not the same file
      :ElseIf hash‚ČĘFileHash file ‚čĄ changed‚Üź1 ‚ćĚ not the same hash - unfortunately, there could be a false negative with CRC32 - e.g. swap two bytes that are offset by 4 bytes : '‚Ćą,‚Ćä'‚Üí'‚Ćä,‚Ćą' or 'A,B,C'‚Üí'C,B,A'
      :EndIf
      :If compsrc ‚čĄ ‚ćĚ need a closer look
          :If 0‚ąä‚ćīfilesrc ‚čĄ filesrc‚ÜźGetFileSource file ‚čĄ :EndIf
          aplsrc‚Üźns GetAplSource(‚äāname),LookupRef ns
          changed‚Üź~CompareSource aplsrc filesrc nc nc2  ‚ćĚ compare source to be sure - will return 1 where whitespace not preserved
      :EndIf
