    ‚ąá r‚ÜźViewMetaData mode
    ‚ćĚ Experiemental function to inspect Link meta data.
    ‚ćĚ For debugging only.
    ‚ćĚ !!! DO NOT USE THIS function in application code!!!
      r‚Üź5177‚Ć∂‚ć¨
      r‚Üź(~(8‚ÜĎ¬®‚ćē¬®2‚äÉ¬®r)‚ąä‚äā'‚éēSE.Link')/r
      r‚Üźr[‚ćč‚ćē‚ĆĹ‚ÜĎ2‚ÜĎ¬®r]
     
      :Select mode
