          ‚Üí0 If code‚ą®.>7         ‚ćĚ case code must be octal digits
          ‚Üí0 If(‚Ćą3√∑‚ć®‚ČĘname)‚Č†(‚ČĘcode)  ‚ćĚ case code must be of correct length
          mask‚Üź‚ĆĹ,‚ćČ2 2 2‚ä§code     ‚ćĚ boolean mask of upper-case
          ‚Üí0 If~(‚äā(‚ČĘname)‚Üďmask)‚ąä‚ć¨(,0)(0 0)  ‚ćĚ mask must be padded with 0-2 zeros
