          path‚Üź(‚ČĘdir)‚Üďpath       ‚ćĚ do not case-code linked directory
          parts‚Üź(Parts path),‚äāfile
          parts‚ÜźCaseCodePart¬®parts      ‚ćĚ case-code each part of path independently
          name‚Üź'/'JoinList(‚äādir),parts
          name,‚Üźext
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá name‚Üź(dir StripCaseCode flatten)name;ext;file;parts;path
    ‚ćĚ strip case code from a file name located under linked dir
