          linkns‚Üź(nss‚ć≥nsref)‚äÉlinks
          :If 0=‚éēNC'linkns.singlefile'
              linkns.singlefile‚Üź0 ‚ćĚ Protect against fake links created by StartupSession
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá links‚Üź{links}LookupLinks nsref;linked;links;mask;nss
    ‚ćĚ lookup which linked namespaces are children of nsref
      :If 900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ links‚ÜźGetLinks ‚čĄ :EndIf
      :If 0‚ąä‚ćīlinks ‚čĄ :Return ‚čĄ :EndIf
      mask‚Üźnsref=nss‚Üź‚ćé¬®links.ns    ‚ćĚ caller must ensure that links can't change   ‚ćĚ nss‚Üź#(0 GetRefTo)¬®links.ns
      :Repeat
          mask‚ą®‚Üźnsref=nss‚Üźnss.##
      :Until ‚ąß/IsRoot nss
      links‚Üźmask/links
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá {opts}‚Üź{defopts}DefaultOpts opts;Check;Default;arrays;mask;modifiers;nl;ok;watch
    ‚ćĚ Get default modifiers for link options namespace
      :If ''‚Č°0‚ćīopts ‚čĄ opts‚Üź‚éēSE.Dyalog.Array.Deserialise opts ‚ćĚ pseudo array notation (experimental)
      :Else ‚čĄ opts‚Üź‚éēSE.Link.‚éēNS opts  ‚ćĚ duplicate namespace to avoid changing caller's, and to avoid having cross-refs between # and ‚éēSE
      :EndIf
      modifiers‚Üź'source' 'watch' 'flatten' 'caseCode' 'forceExtensions' 'forceFilenames' 'arrays' 'sysVars' 'fastLoad' 'beforeWrite' 'beforeRead' 'getFilename' 'customExtensions' 'codeExtensions' 'typeExtensions' 'proceed' 'preloaded' 'ignoreconfig' 'text' 'recordFlags'
      :If ~900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ modifiers,‚Üźdefopts.‚éēNL ¬Į2 ‚čĄ :EndIf
      :If ‚ą®/mask‚Üź~(nl‚Üźopts.‚éēNL ¬Į2)‚ąämodifiers
          Error'Unknown modifiers: ',FmtEach mask/nl
      :EndIf
      Default‚Üźopts.{(‚äÜ‚ćļ){0=‚éēNC‚äā‚ćļ:‚ćé‚ćļ,'‚Üź‚ćĶ'}¬®‚äÜ‚ćĶ}
      :If ~900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ :AndIf ~0‚ąä‚ćīnl‚Üźdefopts.‚éēNL ¬Į2 ‚ćĚ custom defaults go first
          nl Default¬®defopts‚ćé¬®nl
      :EndIf
      Check‚ÜźError{(‚äā‚ćĶ‚ćĶ‚ćé‚ćļ)‚ąä‚ćĶ:_‚Üź1 ‚čĄ ‚ćļ‚ćļ'Invalid value ',(‚ćē‚ćĶ‚ćĶ‚ćé‚ćļ),' for modifier "',‚ćļ,'" - must be one of: ',‚ćē‚ćĶ}opts
      'source'Default'auto' ‚čĄ 'source'Check'auto' 'dir' 'ns'
      'watch'Default'both' ‚čĄ 'watch'Check'both' 'dir' 'ns' 'none'
      'text'Default'aplan' ‚čĄ 'text'Check'aplan' 'plain'
      'flatten' 'caseCode' 'forceExtensions' 'forceFilenames' 'fastLoad' 'sysVars' 'preloaded' 'ignoreconfig' 'recordFlags'Default 0
      'flatten' 'caseCode' 'forceExtensions' 'forceFilenames' 'fastLoad' 'sysVars' 'preloaded' 'ignoreconfig' 'recordFlags'Check¬®‚äā0 1
      Check‚ÜźError{''‚ČĘ0‚ćīv‚Üź‚ćĶ‚ćĶ‚ćé‚ćĶ:‚ćļ‚ćļ'Modifier "',‚ćĶ,'" must be a text vector' ‚čĄ (~0‚ąä‚ćīv)‚ąß(3‚Č†‚éēNC v):Error'Modifier ',‚ćĶ,' must be the name of an APL function' ‚čĄ 1:_‚Üź1}opts
      'beforeWrite' 'beforeRead' 'getFilename'Default'' ‚čĄ Check¬®'beforeWrite' 'beforeRead' 'getFilename'
      Check‚ÜźError{‚ą®/{''‚ČĘ0‚ćī‚ćĶ}¬®‚äÜ‚ćĶ‚ćĶ‚ćé‚ćĶ:‚ćļ‚ćļ'Modifier "',‚ćĶ,'" must be a text vector or vector of text vectors' ‚čĄ 1:_‚Üź1}opts
      'customExtensions'Default''
      'codeExtensions'Default‚äāCODE_EXTENSIONS
      opts.codeExtensions{‚ćĶ‚Üď¬®‚ć®‚ćļ=‚äÉ¬®‚äÜ‚ćĶ}‚ąė‚äÜ‚ć®‚Üź'.'
      Check¬®'customExtensions' 'codeExtensions'
      Check‚ÜźError{v‚Üź‚ćĶ‚ćĶ‚ćé‚ćĶ ‚čĄ error‚Üź'Modifier "',‚ćĶ,'" must be a two-column matrix of name classes (scalar numbers) and extension (text vectors)'
          (2‚Č†‚ČĘ‚ćīv)‚ą®(2‚Č†‚äÉ‚ĆĹ‚ćīv):‚ćļ‚ćļ error ‚čĄ (‚ć¨‚ČĘ0‚ćīv[;1])‚ą®(‚ą®/{''‚ČĘ0‚ćī‚ćĶ}¬®v[;2]):‚ćļ‚ćļ error ‚čĄ 1:_‚Üź1}opts
      'typeExtensions'Default 0 2‚ćī0 ''
      opts.typeExtensions{_‚Üź‚ćļ‚ć™‚ćĶ ‚čĄ _[‚ą™‚ć≥‚ć®‚ä£/_;]}‚Üź‚ÜĎ(2 'apla')(3 'aplf')(4 'aplo')(9.1 'apln')(9.4 'aplc')(9.5 'apli')
      Check'typeExtensions'
      'arrays'Default 0
      :If ~(‚äāarrays‚Üźopts.arrays)‚ąä0 1
          arrays‚Üź,‚äÜ,arrays
          :If ok‚Üź(1=‚ČĘ‚ćīarrays)‚ąß(2=|‚Č°arrays)‚ąß(0=2|‚éēDR‚ąäarrays)‚ąß(1‚ąß.=‚ČĘ¬®‚ćī¬®arrays)
              arrays‚Üź','(‚Č†‚äÜ‚äĘ)‚ąäarrays,[1.5]','  ‚ćĚ allow list of comma-separated names
              ok‚Üź0‚ąä''‚ąė‚ČĘ¬®0‚ćī¬®arrays
          :EndIf
          :If ~ok ‚čĄ Error'Invalid value ',(‚ćēopts.arrays),' for modifier "arrays" - must be 0, 1 or a list of comma-separated names' ‚čĄ :EndIf
          opts.arrays‚Üźarrays
      :EndIf
