              ‚ćĚ :If 0‚ąä‚ćīactname ‚čĄ Error'Internal sniffing error: no name found in script' ‚čĄ :EndIf  ‚ćĚ nope - could well be a tradfn with invalid header
          :Case 0 0 1               ‚ćĚ script : expect name after keyword
              :If ~errors
