    :Section UI
    ‚ćĚ Settings
    WARN‚Üź1     ‚ćĚ flag to enable/disable warnings
    SHOWMSG‚Üź1  ‚ćĚ flag to enable/disable display of log/warning messages
    ‚ćĚ Globals
    WARNLOG‚ÜźDEBUGLOG‚Üź0‚ćī‚äā''  ‚ćĚ actual logs
    LOGSIZE‚Üź1000

    ‚ąá msg‚Üź{caller}(depth FormatMessage)msg
      :If 900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ caller‚Üź0 ‚čĄ :EndIf
      msg‚Üź‚äÜmsg   ‚ćĚ allow building a string as a list of strings to avoid catenating them if not actually using the message
      :If ''‚Č°0‚ćīcaller ‚čĄ msg,‚ć®‚Üźcaller': '  ‚ćĚ caller provided as-is
      :ElseIf ¬Į1‚Č°caller ‚čĄ msg,‚ć®‚Üź(LinkCall ‚ć¨)': '  ‚ćĚ outer link call
      :ElseIf 0‚Č°caller  ‚ćĚ no preprending of call
      :Else ‚čĄ msg,‚ć®‚Üź((1+depth+caller)‚äÉ‚éēXSI)': '  ‚ćĚ look up the stack : 1 is for self, 2 if for one' caller etc
      :EndIf
      msg‚Üź‚äÉ,/,‚ąė‚ćē¬®msg
      :If 0‚ąä(1=‚Č°msg)(1=‚ČĘ‚ćīmsg)(2 0‚ąä‚ć®10|‚éēDR msg)
          Error'Internal error: badly formatted error message'
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá msg‚ÜźTimeStamp msg
      msg,‚ć®‚Üź,'ZI4,</>,ZI2,</>,ZI2,<->,ZI2,<:>,ZI2,<:>,ZI2,<.>,ZI3,< >'‚éēFMT,[0.5]‚éēTS
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá {errno}Error msg;caller
      :If 900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ errno‚ÜźERRNO ‚čĄ :EndIf
      (,‚ćē‚äÉ,/(LinkCall ‚ć¨)': ',‚äÜmsg)‚éēSIGNAL errno
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá {msg}‚Üź{caller}Warn msg
    ‚ćĚ Warn user
      :If ~WARN ‚čĄ :Return ‚čĄ :EndIf
      :If 900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ caller‚Üź‚äĘ ‚čĄ :EndIf
      WARNLOG,‚Üź‚äāTimeStamp msg‚Üźcaller(1 FormatMessage)msg
      WARNLOG‚ÜĎ‚ć®‚Üź-LOGSIZE‚Ćä‚ČĘWARNLOG
      :If SHOWMSG ‚čĄ ‚éē‚Üź'Link Warning: ',msg ‚čĄ :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá {msg}‚Üź{caller}Log msg
    ‚ćĚ Debug information
      :If debug‚Č§0 ‚čĄ :Return ‚čĄ :EndIf
      :If 900‚Ć∂‚ć¨ ‚čĄ caller‚Üź‚äĘ ‚čĄ :EndIf
      DEBUGLOG,‚Üź‚äāTimeStamp msg‚Üźcaller(1 FormatMessage)msg
      DEBUGLOG‚ÜĎ‚ć®‚Üź-LOGSIZE‚Ćä‚ČĘDEBUGLOG
      :If SHOWMSG ‚čĄ ‚éē‚Üź'Link Debug: ',msg ‚čĄ :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá Notify msg
      ‚éē‚Üź'Link @ ',(,'ZI2,<:>,ZI2'‚éēFMT 1 2‚ćī3‚Üď‚éēTS),': ',msg
    ‚ąá


    :EndSection



