      a‚ć™‚Üź'file' 'name of file where item source is stored'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'file1' 'filename to be appended with octal representation of reverse binary encoding of capitalisation'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'item' 'the name of an APL item'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'items' 'one or more names of APL items'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'def' 'expression for one or more APL item values'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'lines' 'line numbers, ‚ć¨ to clear all'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'target' 'a linked namespace, a folder containing a .linkconfig file, or * to set user configuration'
      a‚ć™‚Üź'settings' 'name:value pairs - empty value to delete a setting'
      (args argTxts)‚Üź‚Üď‚ćČa
      myArgs‚Üź'\w+'‚éēS'&'‚äĘinfo.args
      myArgI‚Üź‚äāargs‚ć≥myArgs
      unknown‚ÜźmyArgs~args
